Subject: [gear] ALT Sisyphus

Packaging with gear for ALT Sisyphus.

Dependent branches with upstream sources and patches should be
merged with

    tg update --this-with 'git merge -s ours -m merge-s_ours'

(not that the custom commit message is given as one word, to avoid problems
with splitting).

Maintain .gear/rules in accordance with our TopGit branches for patches.
